column1: #Text=At least I found a lot of people who were very content .
#Text=They may not have an easy life , but they were quite content .
#Text=They 're not a serf class to the aristocracy .
#Text=DS : People dancing in the streets at night .
#Text=I went out at night and I saw a lot of that .
#Text=Much more than those Cubans in Miami .
#Text=DS : My friend I was with was Colombian from Miami , and he made the exact same observation .
#Text=He had a prejudice against Cubans from his time in Miami and he said , "
